# Cloudflare Pages headers for the production web app.
#
# Format reference: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
# Applies on every response served from Pages — preflight (OPTIONS) responses
# share the same headers, so connect-src must include the API origin.
#
# Directive notes
#  - default-src 'self': fall-through deny for anything not enumerated below.
#  - script-src 'self': only first-party scripts. No inline, no eval, no CDNs.
#  - style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline': required by Tailwind's runtime style
#    insertion. We accept the trade-off; XSS via injected style is a much
#    smaller attack surface than via injected script.
#  - img-src 'self' blob: data:: 'blob:' is REQUIRED — decrypted media bytes
#    are exposed to <img> tags through `URL.createObjectURL(...)`. 'data:'
#    covers small inline icons in shadcn/ui.
#  - media-src 'self' blob:: same reason for <video>/<audio> elements that
#    consume decrypted bytes via Object URLs.
#  - connect-src 'self' https://api.hushbox.ai https://*.r2.cloudflarestorage.com
#    https://*.r2.dev wss://api.hushbox.ai: the front-end fetches encrypted
#    blobs directly from R2 via presigned URLs (covers both the
#    `r2.cloudflarestorage.com` S3-compat host and the `*.r2.dev` public
#    hostnames). It also opens a WebSocket to the API for group-chat
#    real-time. 'self' is needed for same-origin /api preflights when the
#    SPA and API share an origin in some preview deployments.
#  - frame-ancestors 'none': hard-deny embedding. Belt-and-suspenders with
#    X-Frame-Options.
#  - base-uri 'self', form-action 'self': close the usual base-tag and
#    form-hijack avenues.
#  - font-src 'self' data:: locally hosted fonts plus inline data: glyphs.
#
# CHANGE CHECKLIST
#  Adding a new external host? Add it under the *narrowest* directive that
#  needs it. Avoid wildcards (`https:`) — they defeat the policy.
#  Adding inline scripts? Don't. Use a hash/nonce path instead, or refactor
#  to a static module.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' blob: data:; media-src 'self' blob:; connect-src 'self' https://api.hushbox.ai https://*.r2.cloudflarestorage.com https://*.r2.dev wss://api.hushbox.ai; font-src 'self' data:; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
